window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Discover the amazing achievements of sports legend Serena Williams - on and off the tennis court - in this exciting new biography.</b> </p> <p>Serena Williams has been ranked number one in the world for tennis singles, won 22 Grand Slam singles titles, and won four Olympic gold medals. She is a powerful player and a fierce competitor. Learn more about the record-breaking athlete in this comprehensive and action-packed biography. </p>"; 
